narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Definitely recommend it. The intensity of it makes you learn the language far faster than people who take L3 and L4 separately.

Take it. The course may sound like a long time, but it's a great way to hang out with a couple other people every morning and just talk in spanish. Much better than the separate L3 and L4 classes, as there is only one section of intensive and only about 7 or 8 people take it.

Excellent. You will learn so much Spanish - much more than in the standard classes - and the small class size and speed allows you to learn while respecting your intelligence and ultimately having a lot of fun.
I would highly recommend it. You're spanish will actually become loads better.
